    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide Fully Funded Armed Security for Jewish Public Buildings ",
        "additional_details": "We are calling for this due to the rise in antisemitism in the UK and a recent terrorist attack in Manchester during Yom Kippur. Jewish schools, synagogues, and community centres face real threats, and we believe it is the state\u2019s duty to provide permanent, funded armed security so that Jewish children and families can live, learn, and worship without fear.",
        "background": "We call upon His Majesty\u2019s Government to urgently provide funding for armed security (police or military presence) at Jewish public buildings \u2013 including schools, synagogues, and community centres.",
